                                                Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd operates within the Petroleum bulk stations & terminals sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd with three other
	miscellaneous retailers and wholesalers in Europe:
		
	IVS Group SA
	
		of Italy
		(2016
	sales of 362.31 million Euro [US$425.24  million]
		of which 82%
		was Italy),
	
	Majestic Wine PLC
	
		of the United Kingdom
		(£402.09 million [US$527.67  million]
		of which 61%
		was Retail), and
	
	Card Factory PLC
	
		which is
		
			also
		
		based in the United Kingdom
		(£381.60 million [US$500.79  million]
		of which 100%
		was Card Retail and Gifts).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	
		During the year ended December of 2016, sales at
		Petrolina (Holdings) Public Ltd were 379.24 million Euro (US$445.11 million).
	
		This
		
			is
		
			a
			
			decrease of 6.3%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 404.85 million Euro.
	

	





 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










